OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes spoke to Eli's parents
OL,8,Fabout their campaign to ensure no
OL,9,Ffamily goes through what they did
OL,11,FThe family of a little boy who died
OL,12,Fafter a gravestone fell on him say
OL,13,Fthey lost their son because of a 200-
OL,14,Fyear-old "status symbol" to someone
OL,15,Fwhose relatives "don't even remember
OL,16,Fthat person".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
