OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,FEli Testa was just four-years-old when
OL,7,Fhe died after the cross on top of a
OL,8,Fgravestone at Rawtenstall Cemetery in
OL,9,FRossendale, Lancashire, fell on top of
OL,10,Fhim on 5 July 2025.
OL,12,FHe was rushed to hospital but died
OL,13,Ffrom his injuries.
OL,15,F"It feels like some kind of sick joke
OL,16,Fthat we have lost a four-year-old boy
OL,17,Ffor a dead person's status symbol,"
OL,18,Fhis dad Thomas Testa said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
