OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1758736074
OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,F"Having monuments that are 10 plus
OL,7,Ffeet tall and that are 200 years old
OL,8,Fand there isn't even a relative that
OL,9,Feven remembers who that person is, it
OL,10,Fjust seems absurd."
OL,12,FThey family are now calling for a
OL,13,Fchange in the law to stop any other
OL,14,Ffamily going through the same thing.
OL,16,F"There was no other child like Eli -
OL,17,Fhe was always bouncing with energy,"
OL,18,Fmum Jessica Testa said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
