OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,F"He loved going to nursery and loved
OL,7,Fhis friends. He was such a sweet and
OL,8,Fhappy little boy - he was just perfect.
OL,10,F"For it just to be taken away, it's
OL,11,Flike the world has now gone silent -
OL,12,Fhe was so loud and energetic."
OL,14,FThomas said "every day is a struggle"
OL,15,Fbut they were trying to "make life as
OL,16,Fnormal as possible" for their two
OL,17,Fother children.
OL,19,FEli's older brother was with him when
OL,20,Fthe gravestone fell.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
