OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,FJessica and Tom are now campaigning
OL,7,Ffor gravestones in cemeteries across
OL,8,Fthe country to be laid flat and
OL,9,Fsecured to the ground, alongside
OL,10,Fmandatory regular checks.
OL,12,FA UK Parliamentary petition has
OL,13,Falready received more than 1,000
OL,14,Fsignatures in support of the change.
OL,16,FIt calls for clearer rules to be set
OL,17,Fout about how headstones are safety
OL,18,Fchecked and the frequency of these
OL,19,Fchecks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
