OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,F"I'd never in a million years think a
OL,7,Fgravestone could just fall," Jess said.
OL,9,F"We want to bring in a law to either
OL,10,Fmake headstones lay flat or that you
OL,11,Fcan only have them a certain height.
OL,13,F"I know they are meant to be checked
OL,14,Fonce a year, but it needs to be more.
OL,16,F"We are calling for this in all
OL,17,Fcemeteries.J"I would feel awful if I
OL,18,Fdidn't do anything now and it happened
OL,19,Fto someone else.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
