OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Rossendale Borough
OL,7,FCouncil, who look after the cemetery,
OL,8,Fexpressed its deepest sympathies,
OL,9,Fadded it recognised the issue is
OL,10,Fsomething councils must take seriously.
OL,12,F"We would like to begin by expressing
OL,13,Four deepest sympathies to Eli's
OL,14,Ffamily," it said.
OL,16,F"We recognise the family's
OL,17,Fdetermination to see changes made so
OL,18,Fthat such a tragedy can never happen
OL,19,Fagain, and we respect the strength it
OL,20,Ftakes to campaign in his memory.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
