OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,F"The safety of cemeteries is a
OL,7,Fresponsibility that all councils must
OL,8,Ftake seriously.
OL,10,F"There is already a legal requirement
OL,11,Ffor councils to regularly inspect
OL,12,Fmemorials and headstones and across
OL,13,Fthe sector we must remain fully
OL,14,Fcommitted to meeting those obligations.
OL,16,F"This is also a sensitive and complex
OL,17,Fissue. Cemeteries are places to visit,
OL,18,Fremember, pay tribute, mourn, and find
OL,19,Fcomfort.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
