OL,3,C'We have lost our four-year-old boy
OL,4,Cfor a dead person's status symbol'
OL,6,F"While many memorials and headstones
OL,7,Fare the responsibility of the families
OL,8,Fwho erected them, all inspections or
OL,9,Frepairs must be approached with care
OL,10,Fand respect with families and
OL,11,Frelatives.
OL,13,F"This can be challenging where records
OL,14,Fare incomplete, or relatives are no
OL,15,Flonger local - something that councils
OL,16,Feverywhere contend with, and
OL,17,Fnationally must work collectively to
OL,18,Faddress."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
